{
 "name": "RPlog_Raid_on_Tatooine",
 "title": "Raid on Tatooine",
 "summary": "On a cool Tatooine night, a slaver gang co-led by the Kajain'sa'Nikto Bil'lay B'hob drinks in a secluded cantina, one boss keeping a chained human girl at his side, unaware that five scout-armored figures are closing in. The disguised raiders -- including the unarmed Twi'lek Tal'sin Secura and the squad leader Bailey, under orders from a Colonel to detain rather than kill -- spring their assault as a brawl explodes into blasterfire and shotgun blasts. Tal'sin grumbles about his hated new combat armor even as he downs gang bosses, while the masked marksman Vaughan and the others cut through the henchmen. The chaotic raid leaves bosses dead or stunned and the gang shattered.",
